islam bank establish 50 mln dlr trade portfolio the islam develop bank ( idb ) and 20 islam bank sign an agreement to establish a 50 mln dlr trade portfolio to financ trade among islam countri , idb sourc said . they said idb 's share in the portfolio , which will onli financ export and import of the privat sector , wa limit to up to 25 mln dlr . the sourc said share in the porfolio could be trade or redeem by the idb , ad that thi wa a major step in establish an islam financ market .